{
  "title": "Richly Seasoned French Lamb Cassoulet",
  "description": "A hearty and flavorful French dish featuring lamb, beans, and a blend of spices, cooked to perfection in a tandoor clay pot. This macrobiotic friendly meal is perfect for a dinner gathering.",
